Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離他遠一點  Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有資格待在遠野身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要制裁你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要袒護她？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛她可是想吸你的血喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！ 一定是你弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直說她不吸血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她討厭血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道她真正的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖的慾望遠比死徒還要深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種吸血衝動不是你所想的那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都是用自身所有的力量拚命壓抑下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會相信這種鬼話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊你原本是Roa…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  現在的她已經沒有力量控制自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容器的大小從一開始就是固定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過長久的時間總有一天會裝滿而溢出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要是容器上出現裂縫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個叫作月之民的非人類種群
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們族裡有一位被稱為白色公主的高貴公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在純白中醒來  在純白中沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何謂污穢之真祖的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個純潔卻造成了悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一條愛上公主的蛇輕聲說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下  請喝下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話口渴的感覺就會立刻消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那是劇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為蛇想得到公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條蛇名叫Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是白色公主墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像起到了相反的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來她自己封印了自己從此只為贖罪而活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贖罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這八百年來她追著Roa的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複著從沉眠中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處決之後又沉眠的輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟任何人接觸只是像機械一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我約會的話就原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟志貴聊各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為志貴在身邊我才會覺得有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是吸血鬼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和志貴會變成什麼樣子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專程出來找我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傷痕呼喚來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了  志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個無情的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前不是常常在一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四季
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四季
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於想起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明被我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你動哥哥一根寒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要袒護冒牌貨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是你把我從那個黑暗的地下牢房放出來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我從這裡放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣讓你連父親都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去殺  去殺  去殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然選擇了遠野的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael Roa Valdamjong
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙為什麼要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不是一樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己的罪深感後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我跟你相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時饒你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是下次我絕不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說  你早就知道一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓哥哥知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我希望你能在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在欺騙哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面寫著一切真相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二月一日  開始實行長久以來的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過半夜之後展開襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七夜村幾乎完全毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了殘存的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他名叫志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟吾兒相同的名字引起我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.40,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：四季和志貴日文發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定收他為養子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七夜是退魔的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的存在對壓抑遠野的血能有幫助就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾兒四季發生異變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對妹妹秋葉揮刀相向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四季殺害了剛好在場的養子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四季完全失去理性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我判斷只能將他處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法殺死四季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然掩蓋了整個事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾兒卻已經不再是人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉把生命分給了養子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把四季和養子的身份做了交換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會變成這樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去殺  去殺  去殺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  你真正想保護的東西出現之時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定會需要它的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格待在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意剛剛的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在我還是忍不住想吸你的血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往我還不是一個人做到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你已經沒有那種力量了  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣跟你在一起實在太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好難過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時你看我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不在乎其他人用那種眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是不希望志貴你那樣看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了你那樣看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你那麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你別說要一個人做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才覺得活著是件快樂的事  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能再讓你自己一個人去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人一起去吧  Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得困擾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴  我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我在那裡等你的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘記？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我殺死的人竟然在那裡笑著等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時心想這一定是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了決心追殺Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻被沒見過的人殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我當時想絕對要讓他嘗嘗同樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那時候我覺得非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我第一次有時間那麼專心的想著某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有殺了我事情會變成什麼樣子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是假設的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還是跟現在一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（再見）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid…
